@startuml 41-screen-reader-streaming
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Screen Reader Announcement for Streaming Chat

actor "SR user" as User
participant "AskModePage\n(aria-live=polite)" as UI
participant "AnnouncementBuffer" as BUF
participant "POST /api/ask (SSE)" as API
participant "Screen reader" as SR

User -> UI: type question, Enter
UI -> UI: append user bubble\ninto live region
UI -> SR: "You said: {question}"
SR --> User: announces once

UI -> API: POST (SSE)
loop tokens
    API --> UI: event: token
    UI -> BUF: append text (hidden)
    UI -> UI: visible bubble updates (for sighted)
end
API --> UI: event: citations / done
UI -> UI: write full buffered answer\ninto live region (atomic)
UI -> SR: announce full answer once
SR --> User: hears answer

UI -> UI: append mini-cards (role=link)\naria-name "Contact: Name, role, similarity S"
UI -> SR: announce each card in order
SR --> User: hears citations

UI -> UI: append follow-up chips (buttons)
UI -> SR: labels equal chip text

note over BUF
  Buffering prevents token-by-token
  firehose announcements.
end note

@enduml
